text: Eurotrash may refer to: * Eurotrash (term), derogatory term used for certain Europeans, especially in the United States * Eurotrash (album), 2001 album of Norwegian industrial rock band Zeromancer * Eurotrash (TV series), late-night British comedy series from 1993 to 2007 * "Eurotrash", 1994 short story by Irvine Welsh in the collection The Acid House * "Eurotrash", 1997 song by Celtic punk band Dropkick Murphys on Boys on the Docks ==See also== *Trailer trash *White trash
title: Eurotrash
